data.title: Rachel Rebibo (podcast interview) — Ticho's Table
data.meta_description: In this episode Jon interviews professional photographer Rachel Rebibo.Rachel shares her thoughts on wildlife conservation, film photography, David Attenborough and more.
data.text:
In this episode Jon interviews professional photographer Rachel Rebibo. Rachel shares her thoughts on wildlife conservation, film photography, David Attenborough and more.

Plus Jon and Val serve up some dinner-table advice to a meek vegan in Vegan W(h)ines.

Mentioned in this Episode:

Wine of the day: Campesino Carmenere from Oxfam Fair Trade

Born Free Foundation award-winning short film The Bitter Bond

Kudu (photo by Rachel on Instagram)

“White veganism”

David Attenborough: A Life on Our Planet (on Netflix)
